---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description =
  'How ChinaTripBox collects, uses, and protects your information, including cookies, advertising, and affiliate disclosures.';
const lastUpdated = 'July 10, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout title={`${title} | ChinaTripBox`} description={description} noindex={false} locale="ja">
  <Header locale="ja" />
  <main class="container-page py-12">
    <article class="prose-content article-body">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p class="mt-4">
        This Privacy Policy explains how ChinaTripBox ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and
        safeguards information when you visit this website. By using this site, you agree to the
        practices described below.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We do not require you to create an account or submit personal information to read our
        content. We may collect limited, non-identifying information automatically, such as browser
        type, device, pages visited, and approximate location derived from your IP address, for the
        purpose of understanding site usage and improving our guides.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you contact us by email, we may receive your name, email address, message content, and
        any information you choose to include. We use this information only to respond to your
        request, review corrections, or manage partnership enquiries.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you use a future AI-assisted travel help feature, your question and related context may
        be processed by a third-party AI provider so that an answer can be generated or summarized.
        Do not submit passport photos, bank card numbers, passwords, PINs, one-time verification
        codes, or other sensitive personal information.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This site uses cookies and similar technologies to enable core functionality, remember your
        preferences, measure traffic, serve advertising, and protect site performance. You can
        control or disable cookies through your browser settings, though some features may not work
        as intended if you do.
      </p>
      <p>
        For visitors in regions where consent is required, including the European Economic Area, the
        United Kingdom, and Switzerland, we may use Google's certified consent management tools or
        another Google-certified consent management platform to request and store your cookie and
        advertising choices.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        We display advertisements to keep this site free. Third-party vendors, including Google, may
        use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites. Google's use
        of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visits. You
        may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
        <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="nofollow">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Google and its partners may process data for ad measurement, fraud prevention, frequency
        capping, personalized advertising, and non-personalized advertising, depending on your
        location and consent choices. You can learn more about how Google uses information from
        sites and apps that use its services at
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" rel="nofollow">Google's partner sites policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics and Performance</h2>
      <p>
        We may use privacy-conscious analytics, hosting logs, or performance tools to understand
        traffic trends, detect errors, and keep the site fast and reliable. These tools may collect
        technical information such as page views, device type, browser, referring page, and general
        region.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you click one and make a purchase, we may
        earn a commission at no additional cost to you. We only recommend products and services we
        believe are genuinely useful to travelers.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our guides link to external websites and services. We are not responsible for the privacy
        practices or content of these third-party sites. We encourage you to review their privacy
        policies.
      </p>

      <h2>AI-Assisted Features</h2>
      <p>
        We may use AI tools to answer simple travel questions, summarize requests, or route complex
        issues for human review. AI responses may be incomplete or inaccurate and should be checked
        against official sources when the decision is important.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can manage cookies through your browser settings, use Google Ads Settings to control ad
        personalization, and contact us if you want to ask about information you previously sent to
        us by email.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We take reasonable measures to protect the information handled through this site. However,
        no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee
        absolute security.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal
        information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page
        with an updated revision date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please reach us via our
        <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
